    a: "All lab-grown diamonds I supply come with an IGI (International Gemological Institute) grading certificate. The report number is laser-inscribed on the stone's girdle so you can independently verify the grade before the ring arrives."
  },
  {
    q: "How long does a custom ring take?",
    a: "4&ndash;6 weeks from design approval. The CAD rendering and revision phase takes 5&ndash;7 business days. Casting and setting takes 10&ndash;15 business days. Shipping typically adds one business day once the ring ships."
